.SS RECURSIVE
.P
The syntax for initiate a \fBrecursive\fR layout is "{}".\&
The content of layout resides within the brackets.\&
\fB:\fR is the delimiter between the outer and inner layout.\& Both are property specific 
to the \fBrecursive\fR layout.\& Only characters are acceptable as layout denominators.\&
.P
It will never and should never give an empty area,
no matter how funky your combinations may be.\&
